    "title": "Configuring media device discovery"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Enable the Media Device Discovery capability in an iOS app extension to indicate its intent to search the local network or paired Bluetooth devices for a third-party media receiver. This capability corresponds to the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/BundleResources/Entitlements/com.apple.developer.media-device-discovery-extension",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " entitlement. When you enable Media Device Discovery, Xcode adds the entitlement to a code-signing entitlements file for the extension’s target.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "At run-time, when a user invokes a UI to play media, the app presents an ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/AVKit/AVRoutePickerView",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " to offer possible devices for the user to stream to. The system searches your app’s bundle for extensions with this entitlement to check whether your app provides such a device. If so, the system adds the third-party device next to any available AirPlay devices in the picker, which provides the user with a unified media streaming experience.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Add-the-Media-Device-Discovery-capability-to-your-target",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Add the Media Device Discovery capability to your target",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To add the capability, follow the steps in the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Xcode/documentation/Xcode/adding-capabilities-to-your-app#Add-a-capability",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": "",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "section of ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Xcode/documentation/Xcode/adding-capabilities-to-your-app",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " for your extension’s target. If you add a new target in your Xcode project using the Media Device Discovery template, Xcode enables this capability automatically.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "media-device-discovery",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Code-the-extension",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Code the extension",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You code the extension to search the local network or paired Bluetooth devices for a specific media receiver using the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/DeviceDiscoveryExtension",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " framework. If the search succeeds, the extension passes the discovered device to the system. For an example app that demonstrates media device discovery, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/DeviceDiscoveryExtension/discovering-a-third-party-media-streaming-device",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
